Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.01,0:00:01.01,cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.52,0:22:44.83,cned,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在呼喚我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.21,0:22:50.50,cned,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在某處呼喚我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.68,0:22:56.05,cned,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溫柔的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.24,0:22:59.77,cned,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從遠方傳來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.94,0:23:02.34,cned,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心為之而動
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.55,0:23:05.71,cned,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.90,0:23:13.28,cned,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這悲傷的預感將是否成真
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.77,0:23:19.19,cned,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未曾知曉的心願
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.37,0:23:26.39,cned,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漸漸浮現
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.61,0:23:32.61,cned,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直有個夢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.79,0:23:38.55,cned,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢中迷惘 而充滿自由
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.76,0:23:44.20,cned,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輕聲許下願望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.41,0:23:49.61,cned,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想和大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.59,0:23:57.28,cned,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相視而笑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.01,0:00:01.01,cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.66,0:24:12.12,cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還在想
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.56,0:24:16.17,cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許和真澄合二為一之後
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.59,0:24:19.09,cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才能更多得陪在你的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.13,0:24:22.36,cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真響
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.69,0:24:26.83,cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父親 父親 你快過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.18,0:24:29.72,cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真夏要被真澄帶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.34,0:24:36.36,cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想成為普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.54,0:24:37.86,cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎
